quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  20,25,"UMûsâ wathi: “O Nkosi yam! Ndandisele isifuba sam (ndibe nokuzithemba)"
  20,26,Undenzele lula umsebenzi wam
  20,27,Ukhulule iqhina elwimini lwam
  20,28,Ukuze bayiqonde intetho yam
  20,29,Ndinyulele kananjalo umncedisi ovela kusapho lwasekhaya
  20,30,"UHârûn (uAron), umntakwethu"
  20,31,“Undongezelele amandla kunye naye
  20,32,Makahlulelane nam ngomsebenzi wokuvakalisa (umyalezo ka-Allâh)
  20,33,Ukuze siKuzukise kakhulu Wena
  20,34,SiKukhumbule kakhulu kananjalo
  20,35,Inene Wena Wahlala Usibona thina.”
  20,36,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Usinikiwe isicelo sakho, wena Mûsâ"
  20,37,Kananjalo inene Thina SaSikhe Sakwenzela inceba kwelinye ilixa (elingaphambili kuneli)
  20,38,Xa Satyhilela umama wakho ngoko Samtyhilela kona
  20,39,"Sathi (kuye): ‘Mfake (umntwana) etyesini, uze uyijule emlanjeni, umlambo wona uyakuyityekezela elunxwemeni; apho ke utshaba lwaM notshaba lwakhe luza kumchola khona.’ Kananjalo wena Ndakunika uthando oluvela kuM lokuba ukhuliswe phantsi kweLiso laM"
  20,40,"Ke kaloku udade wenu ukuhamba kwakhe wathi: ‘Ndinganikhombisa na umntu onokunigcinela yena (umntwana)?’ Sakubuyisela kanjalo ke kumama wakho, khon’ukuze apholise amehlo akhe angakhathazeki. Wena ke wabulala umntu, kodwa Sakusindisa Thina kwimbandezelo enkulu Sakuvavanya ngovavanyo olukhulu. Wena wahlala iqela leminyaka nabantu bakwaMidiyan waza weza apha ngexesha elimisiweyo eNdalimisela wena Mûsâ"
  20,41,Ndikukhethele (ukuba usebenzele) Mna wena (Mûsâ)
  20,42,"Hamba ke wena nomntakwenu neMiqondiso yaM, ningaze niyekelele nityhafe ekuNdikhumbuleni Mna"
  20,43,"Hambani ke nobabini niye kuFir’awn, inene yena sele egabadele"
  20,44,Nithethe naye ngentetho enobulali ukuze mhlawumbi akhumbuzeke oyike uAllâh
  20,45,"Bathi bona: “Nkosi yethu, inene thina soyika ukuba hleze asuke angxame asohlwaye kungenjalo asuke agabadele (ngakumbi ngokuchasene nathi).”"
  20,46,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Musani ukoyika, inene Mna Ndiya kuba nani, Ndiya kuniva Ndinibone nokunibona.”"
  20,47,"Ngoko ke hambani nobabini niye kuye, nithi: ‘Inene, thina singabathunywa beNkosi yakho, ngoko ke khulula aBantwana bakwaSirayeli bahambe nathi, ungabangcungcuthekisi; inene thina, size nomqondiso ovela eNkosini yakho! Kananjalo uxolo luya kuba kwabo balandela isiKhokelo"
  20,48,"Inene, kutyhiliwe kuthi okokuba isohlwayo siya kuba phezu kwalowo uphikayo atshikile.”"
  20,49,"UFir’awn wathi: “Ngubani na ke ngoko Mûsâ iNkosi yenu nobabini?”"
  20,50,"UMûsâ wathi: “INkosi yethu nguloWo Wanika into nganye isimo sayo nendalo yayo, Waza Wayikhokela ngokuthe tye.”"
  20,51,"UFir’awnwathi:“Nithininakengezizukulwanazamandulo?”"
  20,52,"(UMûsâ) wathi: “Ulwazi loko luseNkosini yam, eNcwadini (yaYo). INkosiyamayiyenziimpazamo Ingalibalinakulibala.”"
  20,53,"(Yena) nguloWo Wanenzela umhlaba wangathi ngumandlalo Wanivulela iindlela kuwo apho, Wanithumelela amanzi (imvula) evela esibhakabhakeni. Kananjalo Sivelisa ngawo (amanzi) iintlobontlobo zezityalo"
  20,54,Yidlani nidlise nemfuyo yenu inene kuko oku kukho umqondiso kubantu bengqiqo